1
00:00:50,479 --> 00:00:51,560
I'm guiding you.

2
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:53,399
Do you understand?

3
00:00:56,159 --> 00:00:56,799
Why are you here?

4
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:57,479
Let go!

5
00:01:02,359 --> 00:01:03,240
It's broken, it's broken.

6
00:01:05,640 --> 00:01:06,159
You...

7
00:01:06,519 --> 00:01:07,480
Just you wait!

8
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:08,879
Don't, don't hit me.

9
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:09,760
We're not close.

10
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:10,599
Grandpa, grandpa.

11
00:01:10,799 --> 00:01:11,599
I call you grandpa.

12
00:01:12,079 --> 00:01:12,760
Let go first.

13
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:13,560
Ask her.

14
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:15,920
Ma'am, I'm sorry.

15
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:16,680
Please forgive me.

16
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:18,959
Well done!

17
00:01:19,159 --> 00:01:19,879
Well done!

18
00:01:20,079 --> 00:01:20,640
Well done!

19
00:01:22,319 --> 00:01:23,200
Do you have your phone?

20
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:24,480
Yes.

21
00:01:24,519 --> 00:01:25,040
Call the police.

22
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:26,719
Tell them I harassed you.

23
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,159
No, no need.

24
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:29,760
I forgive you.

25
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:31,920
Is that okay?

26
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:32,680
Okay.

27
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:33,439
Okay.

28
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:34,040
Call the police.

29
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:36,879
Hurry up.

30
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:38,760
Brother.

31
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:39,599
It hurts.

32
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:40,480
Hello.

33
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:41,680
Yes.

34
00:01:41,799 --> 00:01:42,840
Call the police.

35
00:01:52,159 --> 00:01:53,840
I memorized his address

36
00:01:54,359 --> 00:01:55,680
during the mediation at the police station.

37
00:02:02,359 --> 00:02:03,400
Your uncle and him

38
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:05,159
are clearly trying to blackmail you.

39
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:06,959
Your recording won't help.

40
00:02:07,079 --> 00:02:08,039
They won't admit it.

41
00:02:08,439 --> 00:02:09,840
If you want to resolve this,

42
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:11,120
go to his hometown,

43
00:02:11,759 --> 00:02:12,719
find that pregnant woman,

44
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:15,560
and get to the bottom of it.

45
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:17,039
What else do you know?

46
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,960
Wait, how do you know this?

47
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,719
Cai'en told me.

48
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:22,840
Cai'en told you?

49
00:02:25,039 --> 00:02:25,680
You know,

50
00:02:25,879 --> 00:02:28,280
if he gets involved in something shady,

51
00:02:28,439 --> 00:02:30,400
how will he ever hold his head up again?

52
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,680
I can easily come up with 500,000.

53
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,599
I only have one request:

54
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,039
I want to meet that family.

55
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:36,080
I'll make sure you get your share.

56
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,280
If you don't take me to meet them,

57
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,639
you'll be begging on the streets.

58
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,439
You...

59
00:02:43,439 --> 00:02:44,560
Impressive.

60
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,400
After Cai'en told me,

61
00:03:06,639 --> 00:03:07,520
I've been following you

62
00:03:07,879 --> 00:03:08,560
until just now.

63
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,919
Thank goodness she told me.

64
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,639
What if something had happened to you?

65
00:03:14,039 --> 00:03:14,840
What would I have done?

66
00:03:29,439 --> 00:03:31,120
You even got his home address.

67
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,599
When are you two going to dig deep

68
00:03:34,439 --> 00:03:35,319
and get to the bottom of this?

69
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:37,400
Today.

70
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:38,879
Today?

71
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:43,319
It's quite a distance.

72
00:03:44,319 --> 00:03:45,319
It'll be dark by the time you get there.

73
00:03:46,319 --> 00:03:47,439
It's too late to go back.

74
00:03:50,919 --> 00:03:52,000
I'll go by myself. He doesn't have to.

75
00:03:53,159 --> 00:03:54,080
What are you doing?

76
00:03:54,319 --> 00:03:55,240
You're so stubborn.

77
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:58,039
It's good to have a free bodyguard.

78
00:03:58,639 --> 00:03:59,520
Don't be shy.

79
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:00,680
Qingyou.

80
00:04:02,879 --> 00:04:03,560
You're still talking.

81
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:05,080
Well,

82
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,479
why did you tell him?

83
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:07,800
I'm helping you.

84
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:09,360
If I don't tell my brother,

85
00:04:09,599 --> 00:04:10,520
tell Lin Hao?

86
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,000
Don't even think about it.

87
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:14,719
Lin Hao is mine.

88
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,360
Brother.

89
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,560
Thanks.

90
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,519
Next time, make it more convincing.

91
00:04:39,279 --> 00:04:39,800
Let's have the meeting.

92
00:04:40,519 --> 00:04:41,800
Let's finalize the shooting plan today.

93
00:04:41,959 --> 00:04:42,759
I'll join you.

94
00:04:42,959 --> 00:04:44,000
How many scenes do you plan to give me?

95
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:45,160
I plan to cut them all.

96
00:04:51,959 --> 00:04:52,480
What's wrong?

97
00:04:53,279 --> 00:04:55,199
I sprained my ankle.

98
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,759
It hurts.

99
00:05:02,279 --> 00:05:03,079
You can pretend to be injured.

100
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:08,519
You don't look like you're pretending.

101
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:09,920
But you were fooled.

102
00:05:20,519 --> 00:05:21,279
Brother.

103
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,120
You're holding the script upside down.

104
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:32,439
What?

105
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:34,600
He and she...

106
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,279
They...

107
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,879
What's going on with them?

108
00:05:38,199 --> 00:05:38,920
Exes.

109
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,000
Oh my god.

110
00:05:43,519 --> 00:05:45,079
I'm in the same room with my ex.

111
00:06:00,279 --> 00:06:01,720
Don't get me wrong.

112
00:06:03,759 --> 00:06:05,720
I wanted to book two rooms.

113
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,319
But there's a tour group today.

114
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,920
So there's only one room left.

115
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,519
I understand.

116
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,800
Are you comfortable?

117
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,439
Yeah.

118
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,279
OK.

119
00:06:30,279 --> 00:06:31,319
Have a good night.

120
00:06:31,519 --> 00:06:32,639
We need to find someone tomorrow.

121
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:43,959
If the miscarriage of that pregnant woman

122
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:46,000
really had something to do with you,

123
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,079
what would you do?

124
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,079
If it really has something to do with me,

125
00:06:58,519 --> 00:06:59,040
I'll admit it.

126
00:06:59,959 --> 00:07:01,120
I can support her for the rest of her life.

127
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,519
At that time,

128
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,120
I'll leave Changchun,

129
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,079
and stay away from all of you.

130
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,839
Is that why

131
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,160
you don't want to be with me?

132
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:29,600
I...

133
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:30,879
I'm sleepy.

134
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,160
Go to sleep.

135
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,519
Lan Xiaochuan,

136
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:11,040
what do you mean?

137
00:08:13,639 --> 00:08:14,680
Don't pretend to be asleep.

138
00:08:18,959 --> 00:08:19,439
Yunfei,

139
00:08:20,279 --> 00:08:20,720
I...

140
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,199
You've taken the ring.

141
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,120
What do you mean?

142
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,480
You don't want your future, do you?

143
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:40,360
What if my uncle comes to you?

144
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:41,480
You've met him.

145
00:08:42,519 --> 00:08:44,279
You know he'll drag people down with him.

146
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:07,039
Are you trying to get yourself into trouble?

147
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:09,200
I'm determined to get into this trouble.

148
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,519
Then think it through.

149
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,159
You won't be able to get rid of it later.
